OL,3,CEly remembers two teenage boys one
OL,4,Cyear on from their deaths
OL,6,FThe Cardiff community of Ely has come
OL,7,Ftogether to remember best friends
OL,8,FKyrees Sullivan and Harvey Evans one
OL,9,Fyear on from their deaths.
OL,11,FKyrees, 16, and Harvey, 15, were
OL,12,Friding an electric bike when they
OL,13,Ffatally crashed on Snowden Road
OL,14,Fshortly after 6pm on May 22, 2023.
OL,16,FCCTV footage later circulated showing
OL,17,Fpolice were following the boys in a
OL,18,Fmarked police van just minutes before
OL,19,Fthe crash, prompting unrest in the
OL,20,Farea into the early hours of the
OL,21,Ffollowing day.
