OL,3,CEly remembers two teenage boys one
OL,4,Cyear on from their deaths
OL,6,FLoved ones of the two best friends and
OL,7,Fmembers of the community gathered on
OL,8,Fthe evening of May 22 at the scene to
OL,9,Fremember the young boys.
OL,11,FPolice involvement in the incident has
OL,12,Fbeen subject to two watchdog
OL,13,Finvestigations.
OL,15,FLast week, the Independent Office for
OL,16,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) said its
OL,17,Finvestigation into the interaction
OL,18,Fbetween South Wales Police and the two
OL,19,Fteens before their deaths was in its
OL,20,Ffinal stages.
