OL,3,CEly remembers two teenage boys one
OL,4,Cyear on from their deaths
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police referred itself to
OL,7,Fthe watchdog over the police van being
OL,8,Fseen on CCTV travelling close behind
OL,9,Fthe bike prior to the fatal incident.
OL,11,FThe IOPC said all lines of enquiry in
OL,12,Fits investigation were nearly complete.
OL,14,FA second investigation has centred
OL,15,Faround complaints raised by the
OL,16,Ffamilies of the boys, with complaints
OL,17,Fcentring around the police response
OL,18,Fand management of the collision scene,
OL,19,Fhow the families were dealt with at
OL,20,Fthe scene and the way in which South
OL,21,FWales
