OL,3,CEly remembers two teenage boys one
OL,4,Cyear on from their deaths
OL,6,FPolice communicated with them
OL,7,Ffollowing the boys' deaths. The IOPC
OL,8,Fsay this probe is nearing completion.
OL,10,FA month after the incident, the IOPC
OL,11,Fserved gross misconduct notices on the
OL,12,Fdriver and passenger of the police
OL,13,Fvan. In August last year, it also
OL,14,Fnotified the driver of the van that
OL,15,Fthey were under criminal investigation
OL,16,Ffor alleged dangerous driving. It said
OL,17,Fthese notices do not necessarily mean
OL,18,Fthat any disciplinary or criminal
OL,19,Fproceedings will follow.
