OL,3,CEly remembers two teenage boys one
OL,4,Cyear on from their deaths
OL,6,FIOPC director David Ford said: "As we
OL,7,Fapproach the one-year anniversary of
OL,8,Fthe tragic events which took place on
OL,9,Fthe evening of 22 May, I understand
OL,10,Fthat this will be an especially
OL,11,Fdifficult time for the families of
OL,12,FKyrees and Harvey. Our thoughts and
OL,13,Fsympathies continue to be with
OL,14,Feveryone who has been affected by the
OL,15,Floss of such young lives.
