OL,3,CEly remembers two teenage boys one
OL,4,Cyear on from their deaths
OL,6,F"I appreciate the patience shown by
OL,7,Fthe families, stakeholders and the
OL,8,Fwider community of Ely over the last
OL,9,F12 months as the investigations to
OL,10,Festablish exactly what happened have
OL,11,Fprogressed. Our investigations are
OL,12,Fnearing completion and whilst I fully
OL,13,Frecognise the importance of finalising
OL,14,Four investigations, thoroughness
OL,15,Fcannot be compromised.
