OL,3,CEly remembers two teenage boys one
OL,4,Cyear on from their deaths
OL,6,F"Our regular updates to the boys'
OL,7,Ffamilies and South Wales Police
OL,8,Fcontinue as we near the end of both
OL,9,Finvestigations. Following their
OL,10,Fconclusion, we will take decisions
OL,11,Fabout any potential referrals to the
OL,12,FCrown Prosecution Service to consider
OL,13,Fpossible criminal proceedings, as well
OL,14,Fas potential future disciplinary
OL,15,Fmatters. We will also take into
OL,16,Faccount any improvements and learning
OL,17,Fthat may have been identified during
OL,18,Four investigations, whether that's for
OL,19,Findividual officers, or South Wales
OL,20,FPolice on a force-wide basis."
